{"tid":147533,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"(極醜惡) 一隻關於黑警既boardgame","createTime":"2017-03-08T02:15:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-29T07:56:01.000Z","uid":43487,"like":87,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"64ad00e5e9f6a8f6e467de0c1d18b285d14f61fd","tid":147533,"uid":43487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T02:15:29.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我地整緊隻board game , 背景係關於香港警察6~70年代貪污既事績<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成隻game 分左三個陣營<br />\n黑警，黑警隊長，同探長<br />\n玩法係黑警要收集探長既罪證同埋指證佢<br />\n黑警隊長要搵槍殺左探長擺脫佢既控制<br />\n探長要賄賂曬所有黑警令所有人受佢控制<br />\n<br />\n我地自己整左d 卡既圖，大致係咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/00sQ15y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F00sQ15y.jpg&h=437daa83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/53N4p47.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F53N4p47.jpg&h=8b050db2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/644404A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F644404A.jpg&h=b0efd813&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O2c3560.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO2c3560.jpg&h=9dce9f07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cD2xbT7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcD2xbT7.jpg&h=11616069&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k7Ei6hu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk7Ei6hu.jpg&h=09eecd01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家我地想搵人試game/俾d comment<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我地仲想搵個designer執執個layout 同d 圖，唔知有冇人可以幫手，唔會要你白做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可以email或者FB pm我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nemail: headblownstudio@gmail.com<br />\nfb: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/headblownstudio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fheadblownstudio&d=LSsgDEuqvL%2F6lC7PehFbgwdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=592d3ccb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/headblownstudio</a><br />\nig: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/headblownstudio/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fheadblownstudio%2F&d=LSsgDEuqvL%2F6lC7PehFbgwdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=921c9c26\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/headblownstudio/</a>"},{"pid":"a6af15c6381cadab64dd84d0d839a388c863bab4","tid":147533,"uid":45315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T02:17:15.000Z","msg":"push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f97fa22edeaa72efc3bbaab25c846b2df40cffd8","tid":147533,"uid":37771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T02:19:22.000Z","msg":"巴打有冇查過法律？ 用真人相未經同意可能犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申： 唔識法律"},{"pid":"110ff7ca54cefeebb6fbda2174f83671ad35722b","tid":147533,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T02:19:35.000Z","msg":"ICAC呢？"},{"pid":"df318a9733e6fdaf5b43defa1594f0930b4a9baf","tid":147533,"uid":39541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T02:20:24.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9a6455b3c15251f4e7d536442dbd9ae74d0613db","tid":147533,"uid":43487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T02:21:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打有冇查過法律？ 用真人相未經同意可能犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申： 唔識法律</blockquote><br />\n其實我地都有諗過呢個問題, 所以想搵人執執佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor