/> <br />\n又唔會贏</blockquote><br />\n每個回合個個玩家都會收到order要做兩個task, 達成唔到就當out game<br />\n我地會有個類似trading既phase,  俾玩家交換手頭上既task牌去完成個order<br />\n但係trading個時探長有機會乘機賄賂人, 而你就要估邊個係探長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffef7966330aa5b8267e8b17a605248c0aa7e7e4","tid":147533,"uid":55425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T10:51:18.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"cee03025bdc36b7ed6e9489d38b5d9a2afa020c6","tid":147533,"uid":43487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T01:21:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"835f37b478c1a4dff503fa213f645e7e8bb4b9d6","tid":147533,"uid":20820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T01:25:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00c9431696e6f9a190bf273db46c89cef9296d0d","tid":147533,"uid":6153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T01:26:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7fbc83410e0fedeba3a9f921737261b65e0d4f41","tid":147533,"uid":9924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T01:27:55.000Z","msg":"聽落都覺得唔平衡"},{"pid":"8547aeb32b9044bcd2220f9dc5dc4a9da6b4fd9c","tid":147533,"uid":1348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T01:32:54.000Z","msg":"除暴go"},{"pid":"0d64b107fc7f86c2150bc461502d8fd459b9f44b","tid":147533,"uid":43487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T01:39:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽落都覺得唔平衡</blockquote><br />\n我地仲盡量調整緊, 想搵多d人試game俾多d意見我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e155eed689662d6c001be5a985d8d17d2d32006","tid":147533,"uid":84307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T02:29:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/fa