147533,"uid":74908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T10:16:39.000Z","msg":"未得閒睇，留定名先"},{"pid":"d8ec56197c2f8ccb46c4bb768fcc1580809eff0f","tid":147533,"uid":34147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T13:37:34.000Z","msg":"可以幫手試玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bd96dacd1842abd4a379129d36b25fa5db925d6","tid":147533,"uid":31515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T13:40:25.000Z","msg":"探長俾兩個陣型圍？"},{"pid":"348c43290c436935588dcf94cb7c582cf66839c8","tid":147533,"uid":89194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T14:12:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴打有冇查過法律？ 用真人相未經同意可能犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申： 唔識法律</blockquote><br />\n其實我地都有諗過呢個問題, 所以想搵人執執佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無犯法，放心"},{"pid":"d8919abb23e6502f50138acff7e354bd83a8204a","tid":147533,"uid":43487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T03:44:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>巴打有冇查過法律？ 用真人相未經同意可能犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申： 唔識法律</blockquote><br />\n其實我地都有諗過呢個問題, 所以想搵人執執佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無犯法，放心</blockquote><br />\n真係冇? 因為我地都唔清楚呢d版權要點定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"832cd6388d430a04f140ad43c185333a181a7caa","tid":147533,"uid":43487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T03:45:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>探長俾兩個陣型圍？</blockquote><br />\n可以咁講, 但係大家隱藏身份, 同埋trading個時會有誤導成份"},{"pid":"92eb8cf0b97a6aac4224e9663bea7d51434b5d2e","tid":147533,"uid":43487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T03:47:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>聽落都覺得唔平衡</blockquote><br />\n我地仲盡量調整緊, 想搵多d人試game俾多d意見我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實你連基本玩法都無係度講<br />\n想點叫人幫</blockquote><br />\n我地執一執會擺埋上嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"328082d3ce82f6779297b73739e54b5fa621f5e5","tid":147533,"uid":9105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T03:52:20.000Z","msg":"起碼講一講詳細玩法先<br />\n<br />\n如果唔你d圖幾正都無用"},{"pid":"f551cbe13986cad4b442ccd143afaea43c057591","tid":147533,"uid":66555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T04:00:23.000Z","msg":"留名跟進"},{"pid":"51c212a0b467d78141f125c865e57f243061412e","tid":147533,"uid":648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T04:12:23.000Z","msg":"graphic有啲唔match<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3850daefcc69036ba805a53e8cbcbd19c93b7c42","tid":147533,"uid":43487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T04:46:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>graphic有啲唔match<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打有冇咩意見咩方向執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n太明亮/太暗, d icon太怪?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17f5e2aca92c11bfea62c98a0d879843379e55d3","tid":147533,"uid":43487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T05:04:00.000Z","msg":"大概玩法就係遊戲分三班唔同黑警<br />\n<br />\n黑警, 黑警隊長同埋探長<br />\n<br />\n佢地每一回合都會收到張order去做野, 例如係去捉兩個黑社會<br />\n咁每個人都要諗盡方法去完成張order, 唔理你去搶又好, 去老屈人又好都要完成, 如果唔係到最後就會被炒(out game)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n完成order方法主要係透過同其他黑警去交換工作 (互相蛇王), 咁係交換工作嘅同時, 會收到一張賄賂卡<br />\n至於點分別身份, 就要靠呢張賄賂卡<br />\n賄賂卡分兩種, 一張係有錢既, 一張係冇錢既<br />\n黑警只會傳冇錢既賄賂卡, 黑警隊長只會傳有錢既, 探長可以選擇傳有錢/冇錢既都得<br />\n<br />\n唔同陣營就要完成唔同條件去贏, 但係要小心既係黑警收得太多有錢既賄賂卡就會被迫投靠黑警隊長陣營, 當所有人都變左黑警隊長陣營既人(除左探長)就當探長贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n三邊陣營其實可以互相制衡, 唔會話邊一邊圍邊一邊咁<br />\n玩緊果陣你要估下邊一個係咩身份, 因為你要搵到同陣營嘅朋友先有機會贏<br />\n但同時對面亦有可能扮係你朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac53d19628786153015629edf8b9dc05329ef19e","tid":147533,"uid":43487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T05:04:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>telegram?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\ntelegram : manhbs<br />\n<br />\n如果唔想email/fb/ig既, 可以telegram聯絡我地, 盡快回覆你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"243a7987ee92ca797c124d5dd09f664cf5808824","tid":147533,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T05:29:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8833ad5f4b9cef6fbb17392215ed3ec7be41966e","tid":147533,"uid":1391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T06:30:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40e493c3b37a52b347c0baeb173fe9521098fb7a","tid":147533,"uid":43487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T07:18:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41128abeeba9e812ba2e2c7c595aa5ae2e950bf8","tid":147533,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T07:26:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁講法<br />\n黑警玩家受賄有咩著數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又唔會贏</blockquote><br />\n每個回合個個玩家都會收到order要做兩個task, 達成唔到就當out game<br />\n我地會有個類似trading既phase,  俾玩家交換手頭上既task牌去完成個order<br />\n但係trading個時探長有機會乘機賄賂人, 而你就要估邊個係探長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁點解黑警要受賄先<br />\n佢唔受賄都可以估"},{"pid":"8781484cb0d86084f56b4246b947f83eebba468f","tid":147533,"uid":79636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T07:29:20.000Z","msg":"人物唔好用真名, 圖就最好漫畫化."},{"pid":"6fdf41e0036e37dfd0c91002eacf7037c56ef286","tid":147533,"uid":75765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T07:43:48.000Z","msg":"陣營任務有啲怪， 我會咁諗&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n警司: 非法勾當&gt;增加影響力，收買警察以減少留下罪證; <br />\n警察:可做雙方任務， 儲夠錢可走人或轉污點證人， 否則會被入罪或被滅口<br />\n探長: 收集罪證，可以脅迫警察供出警司為目標"},{"pid":"0a1725f2812359c68893f632d4214ff55dc51d0d","tid":147533,"uid":43487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T07:49:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁講法<br />\n黑警玩家受賄有咩著數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又唔會贏</blockquote><br />\n每個回合個個玩家都會收到order要做兩個task, 達成唔到就當out game<br />\n我地會有個類似trading既phase,  俾玩家交換手頭上既task牌去完成個order<br />\n但係trading個時探長有機會乘機賄賂人, 而你就要估邊個係探長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁點解黑警要受賄先<br />\n佢唔受賄都可以估</blockquote><br />\n<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁講法<br />\n黑警玩家受賄有咩著數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又唔會贏</blockquote><br />\n每個回合個個玩家都會收到order要做兩個task, 達成唔到就當out game<br />\n我地會有個類似trading既phase,  俾玩家交換手頭上既task牌去完成個order<br />\n但係trading個時探長有機會乘機賄賂人, 而你就要估邊個係探長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁點解黑警要受賄先<br />\n佢唔受賄都可以估</blockquote><br />\n完成order方法主要係透過同其他黑警去交換工作 (互相蛇王), 咁係交換工作嘅同時, 會收到一張賄賂卡<br />\n至於點分別身份, 就要靠呢張賄賂卡<br />\n賄賂卡分兩種, 一張係有錢既, 一張係冇錢既<br />\n黑警只會傳冇錢既賄賂卡, 黑警隊長只會傳有錢既, 探長可以選擇傳有錢/冇錢既都得"},{"pid":"a473d3ea8cd3ab80bbe0867bbbb598954beddf3b","tid":147533,"uid":43487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T07:49:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁講法<br />\n黑警玩家受賄有咩著數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又唔會贏</blockquote><br />\n每個回合個個玩家都會收到order要做兩個task, 達成唔到就當out game<br />\n我地會有個類似trading既phase,  俾玩家交換手頭上既task牌去完成個order<br />\n但係trading個時探長有機會乘機賄賂人, 而你就要估邊個係探長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁點解黑警要受賄先<br />\n佢唔受賄都可以估</blockquote><br />\n完成order方法主要係透過同其他黑警去交換工作 (互相蛇王), 咁係交換工作嘅同時, 會收到一張賄賂卡<br />\n至於點分別身份, 就要靠呢張賄賂卡<br />\n賄賂卡分兩種, 一張係有錢既, 一張係冇錢既<br />\n黑警只會傳冇錢既賄賂卡, 黑警隊長只會傳有錢既, 探長可以選擇傳有錢/冇錢既都得"},{"pid":"b55a423a85018fe98572fb7ca409da0c71aa956a","tid":147533,"uid":43487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T07:51:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人物唔好用真名, 圖就最好漫畫化.</blockquote><br />\n人物唔會用真名, 圖我地都諗住搵人執過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b94c4c2a5c1e316f41f90f087a567628105dc34a","tid":147533,"uid":43487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T07:53:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>陣營任務有啲怪， 我會咁諗&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n警司: 非法勾當&gt;增加影響力，收買警察以減少留下罪證; <br />\n警察:可做雙方任務， 儲夠錢可走人或轉污點證人， 否則會被入罪或被滅口<br />\n探長: 收集罪證，可以脅迫警察供出警司為目標</blockquote><br />\n你既意思係勝利條件?"},{"pid":"1c768312f3f90071f5ff4ad186c0de2a964bbe25","tid":147533,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T07:55:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁講法<br />\n黑警玩家受賄有咩著數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又唔會贏</blockquote><br />\n每個回合個個玩家都會收到order要做兩個task, 達成唔到就當out game<br />\n我地會有個類似trading既phase,  俾玩家交換手頭上既task牌去完成個order<br />\n但係trading個時探長有機會乘機賄賂人, 而你就要估邊個係探長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁點解黑警要受賄先<br />\n佢唔受賄都可以估</blockquote><br />\n完成order方法主要係透過同其他黑警去交換工作 (互相蛇王), 咁係交換工作嘅同時, 會收到一張賄賂卡<br />\n至於點分別身份, 就要靠呢張賄賂卡<br />\n賄賂卡分兩種, 一張係有錢既, 一張係冇錢既<br />\n黑警只會傳冇錢既賄賂卡, 黑警隊長只會傳有錢既, 探長可以選擇傳有錢/冇錢既都得</blockquote><br />\n即係話黑警只能揀Trade唔Trade賄賂卡，但如收到賄賂卡發現有錢就=已受賄，係唔係咁<br />\n<br />\n咁點知係咪已經所有人受賄"},{"pid":"e313caa083c94d03f3c974543669d3cc6c616ed3","tid":147533,"uid":43487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T08:02:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁講法<br />\n黑警玩家受賄有咩著數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又唔會贏</blockquote><br />\n每個回合個個玩家都會收到order要做兩個task, 達成唔到就當out game<br />\n我地會有個類似trading既phase,  俾玩家交換手頭上既task牌去完成個order<br />\n但係trading個時探長有機會乘機賄賂人, 而你就要估邊個係探長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁點解黑警要受賄先<br />\n佢唔受賄都可以估</blockquote><br />\n完成order方法主要係透過同其他黑警去交換工作 (互相蛇王), 咁係交換工作嘅同時, 會收到一張賄賂卡<br />\n至於點分別身份, 就要靠呢張賄賂卡<br />\n賄賂卡分兩種, 一張係有錢既, 一張係冇錢既<br />\n黑警只會傳冇錢既賄賂卡, 黑警隊長只會傳有錢既, 探長可以選擇傳有錢/冇錢既都得</blockquote><br />\n即係話黑警只能揀Trade唔Trade賄賂卡，但如收到賄賂卡發現有錢就=已受賄，係唔係咁<br />\n<br />\n咁點知係咪已經所有人受賄</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該話大家係互相trade 佢地嘅工作，但一旦trade 左， 對方就有機會賄賂你<br />\n我地最後會有個階段去check 番大家係唔係已經受晒賄賂"},{"pid":"fc94766eaf38d013ee4fb8c56bb70192e960d03b","tid":147533,"uid":63297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T09:02:32.000Z","msg":"Cm game prototyping<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"944a3d496ff1b7363c1c9158fa3e03aedf29f3e6","tid":147533,"uid":33984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T09:03:08.000Z","msg":"help pish"},{"pid":"320a8357b1c3d1cd9e3697d466f91fd0a60957c0","tid":147533,"uid":43487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T09:49:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Cm game prototyping<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我地整左個可以試既prototype架啦, 有興趣試可以fb/tg/email/ig聯絡我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fff551c010ce12e5283b3787f986d035a8d80f09","tid":147533,"uid":43487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T16:38:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73e9712c012801ec68af6d4143219799e225dc55","tid":147533,"uid":42835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T18:24:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Cm game prototyping<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我地整左個可以試既prototype架啦, 有興趣試可以fb/tg/email/ig聯絡我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n痛興趣"},{"pid":"cb0285cc04d1ca12cb327065d7b0ce57372ca1db","tid":147533,"uid":49444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017